{"tid":238122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"妙齡女海邊飲悶酒 路人擔心跳海報警","createTime":"2017-05-10T22:14:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T01:23:44.000Z","uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d298ab8996d639c03523af479d593e6bcd37214e","tid":238122,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T22:14:56.000Z","msg":"妙齡女海邊飲悶酒 路人擔心跳海報警<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0511 05:53<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170511/large/1494453161_782d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170511%2Flarge%2F1494453161_782d.jpg&h=e763eb25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n海邊飲悶酒女子送院治理。(潘志能攝)<br />\n<br />\n清晨近5時，一名年約20多歲女子，獨自在大角嘴浪澄灣對開海邊飲悶酒，途人擔心她有意外於是報警。警方及消防到場，將她勸服送院檢查。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170511/large/1494453874_3c63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170511%2Flarge%2F1494453874_3c63.jpg&h=e2130bc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大角嘴浪澄灣對開海邊。(黃江奇攝)<br />\n<br />\n轉貼自: <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170511/56678350\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170511%2F56678350&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=cad5e40e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170511%2F56678350&h=4b3402e1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170511/56678350</a>"},{"pid":"bf24f269e4ddc1363628a193a70aad1a47f70ccb","tid":238122,"uid":102056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T22:15:55